The '''Australian Political Studies Association''' ('''APSA''') is a professional association for teachers and researchers of political science in [[Australia]] or [[New Zealand]]. It publishes the ''[[Australian Journal of Political Science]]'' (''AJPS'') and host a regular Annual Conference.<ref>[http://www.auspsa.org.au/ Australian Political Studies Association] (Accessed Dec 2010)</ref>

