{{Infobox person | image = | caption = | birth_date ={{birth year and age|1947}} | birth_place =[[Transvaal Province|Transvaal]], [[South Africa]] | death_date = | death_place = | occupation = [[actress]], [[Model (people)|Model]], [[Ballet|ballerina]] }}
'''Ingrid Boulting''' was born in [[Transvaal Province|Transvaal]] in 1947<ref name="Willis1999">{{cite book|last=Willis|first=John|title=Screen World 1998|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2Fj7VqqCpLYC&pg=PA270|accessdate=19 March 2012|date=1999-02-01|publisher=Hal Leonard Corporation|isbn=9781557833419|pages=270–}}</ref> – step-daughter of English film-maker [[Roy Boulting]] and niece of [[John Boulting]] and [[Peter Cotes|Sydney Boulting a.k.a. Peter Cotes]]. She was a ballerina and model,<ref name="Gross2011">{{cite book|last=Gross|first=Michael|title=Model: The Ugly Business of Beautiful Women|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oc2utNlf_AYC&pg=PA224|accessdate=19 March 2012|date=2011-09-27|publisher=HarperCollins|isbn=9780062067906|pages=224–}}</ref> before embarking on an acting career. In 1976, Ingrid starred in ''[[The Last Tycoon (1976 film)|The Last Tycoon]]'', the last film directed by famed director [[Elia Kazan]], written by [[Harold Pinter]] based on [[F. Scott Fitzgerald]]'s Hollywood novel ''[[The Last Tycoon]]'', and produced by [[Sam Spiegel]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Takken|first=Wilbert|title=Every Elia Kazan Movie: The Last Tycoon (1976)|url=http://everyeliakazanmovie.blogspot.com/2013/01/the-last-tycoon-1976.html|accessdate=23 May 2013}}</ref>
==Modeling== Boulting was the iconic face of Biba Cosmetics on the 1968 poster designed by Steve Thomas and photographed by Sarah Moon for [[Barbara Hulanicki]]'s store [[Biba]] in London – the face behind black lace net veil looming out of darkness.
==Movies== * ''[[The Witches (1966 film)|The Witches]]'' (1966) (billed as Ingrid Brett) * ''[[The Jokers]]'' (1967) * ''[[Inadmissible Evidence (film)|Inadmissible Evidence]]'' (1968) * ''[[Kampf um Rom I]]'' (1968) * ''Kampf um Rom II'' (1969)<ref>''[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0064534/?ref_=tt_rec_tti Kampf um Rom II]'' (1969)</ref> * ''[[The Last Tycoon (1976 film)|The Last Tycoon]]'' (1976) * ''Conversations with God'' (2006)<ref>[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0489682/ ''Conversations with God'' (2006)]</ref>
==Current life and career== Boulting is an artist and yoga instructor in [[Ojai, California]]. She is the founder and owner of Sacred Space Studio.
