The '''University Pastoral Center''' ('''Univerzitné pastoračné centrum''') in [[Bratislava]], [[Slovakia]] is the [[Slovakia|Slovak]] equivalent of a  [[Newman's center]], University [[chaplaincy]], [[Campus ministry]] or a similar  [[Roman Catholic Church]] institution for students and youth. It is situated in the city near the universities.

